Package org.agh

Class LibraryTest

java.lang.Object
org.agh.LibraryTest
class LibraryTest extends Object
Integration tests for the Library class verifying a correct solution to the Readersâ€“Writers synchronization problem.

These tests validate:

  • Maximum number of concurrent readers
  • Exclusive access for writers
  • Correct waiting behavior for readers and writers
  • Proper thread creation using virtual threads

CountDownLatch and Awaitility are used instead of Thread.sleep() to ensure deterministic and reliable test execution.
